It's the conductance matrix.

00:36:35.380 --> 00:36:38.050
And it's the equation
that a big finite element

00:36:38.050 --> 00:36:43.490
code, a circuit simulation
code-- It's the matrix

00:36:43.490 --> 00:36:45.870
